img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vektorler-ders-notlari.jpg\" alt=\"vektörler ders notları\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the orthogonal coordinate system A (0,1), B (3,4), [AB] perpendicular [BC], | AC | if; What is the BC.CA product?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/vektorler-ders-notlari-geometri.jpg\" alt=\"vektörler ders notları geometri\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vectors continuation of the question solution …</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Geometry Notes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '196-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-02-21 12:29:19', '2022-02-21 09:29:19', '', 196, 'http://localhost/geometri/?p=198', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
