(217, 1, '2022-02-21 13:13:43', '2022-02-21 10:13:43', '<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/geometri-sorulari-040.jpg\" alt=\"geometri soruları\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Question 40-) ABC and KCN are each triangle, [AD] perpendicular [BN], | AD | = | KN |, | AK | = | KC | if; What is the measure of the KNB angle?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/geometri-sorulari-041.jpg\" alt=\"geometri soruları\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\">Question 41-) ABC is a triangle, [BA] perpendicular [AC], | AD | = | BE | = | EC |, if m (CBA) = 30 °; How many degrees is m (DCE) = α?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/geometri-sorulari-042.jpg\" alt=\"geometri soruları\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\">Question 42-) If ABC is a triangle, [PA] perpendicular [AC], m (BAP) = 15 °, m (ACP) = 25 °; | PC | / | AB | What is the rate?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://www.dersgeometri.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/geometri-sorulari-043.jpg\" alt=\"geometri soruları\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\">Question 43-) ABC is a triangle, [BK] perpendicular [AC], | BL | = | LC |, | BK | = | AL | if; How many degrees is m (LAC) = x?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-bloc